{"tid":1354031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"先拆你屋","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:02:07.000Z","uid":285112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6b93757f289fa4cd40cdc6f3e7c2db36c8ff5f","tid":1354031,"uid":285112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"班圍村佬講到自己僭建係理所當然一樣<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/NEWS/20150517/HK-gaa1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fhtm%2FNEWS%2F20150517%2FHK-gaa1_r.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=e4fa3a3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/NEWS/20150517/HK-gaa1_r.htm</a><br />\n唔通偷偷地吸毒吸咗十幾二十年，就會自動變成合法？<br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄諗到乜嘢辦法，去政府度投訴到佢哋唔拆唔得？<br />\n林鄭想我哋市民鬥市民，我地一於要政府鬥返圍村佬。 <br />\n<br />\n一句講曬:鬼叫你條村突然間咁出名咩。<br />\n精人出口，笨人出手嘅道理都唔知。你有冇見阿妖叫人匿埋喺佢自己條村度吖！<br />\n<br />\n僭建 &gt; 祖墳 &gt; 祠堂"},{"pid":"326536683fd506c663afcd6f2fff9d99fdadcd76","tid":1354031,"uid":285112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}